    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034670/extras/565403cbaf5a68ae99033fc7ee536b08.webp?t=1763486329\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034670/extras/565403cbaf5a68ae99033fc7ee536b08.poster.avif?t=1763486329\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=150 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been captured and enslaved by the Facility and tasked with retrieving blood from overgrown brains from the depths of an ancient megastructure, but you may not be alone down there... Will you accept your fate, or find a way to escape? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abrasion is a first-person horror game set inside a brutal, skyless, megastructure. It takes around 90 minutes to complete. The world is filled with useful items, environmental storytelling, and many secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A dynamic, stalking AI monster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An interconnected world full of hidden passages and secret areas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Diverse items and tools to help you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deep worldbuilding enhanced by intricately designed visuals and audio.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An unsettling story told through the game's environments.</p></li></ul>",
